      • fileReader

        public void fileReader()
        The reader method. The method first reads the file and add the objects into the tree. Then prints the requirements of the homework to the console.

      • authorNames

        public void authorNames()
        This method prints the usable author names to the console. First it takes all the author names. Then it gets rid of the duplicate names. Lastly, prints the elements of the array without nulls.

      • directorNames

        public void directorNames()
        This method prints the usable director names to the console. First it takes all the author names. Then it gets rid of the duplicate names. Lastly, prints the elements of the array without nulls.

      • minPriBook

        public void minPriBook()
        This method finds the minimum priced book of the given author from the console. It takes the author name and search for his/her books. When it finds the books, it compares the prices. Lastly, prints the minimum priced one.

      • maxPriBook

      • priLess
